  "texts": [
    "The results for unbranded content revealed the powerful marketing writing capabilities of generative AI as in Study 1B.",
    "ChatGPT 4 was able to generate texts with slightly higher levels of embodied cognition and lexical diversity.",
    "Moreover, human judges rated the post with text by ChatGPT 4 as having better quality and expressed a higher purchase intention towards it.",
    "The findings implied that ChatGPT 4 might surpass certain Instagram copywriters.",
    "Regression analysis was conducted to examine the impact of key variables (embodied cognition, affect, and lexical diversity) on engagement and purchase intention, with the key variables as independent variables and engagement/purchase intention as dependent variables."
